Author: staps
Title: [ANN][ICO]STAPS - PLATFORM FOR CONVERTING STEPS INTO CRYPTOCURRENCY
Body: Poject terms: Staps - project name, token name Staps Platform - a blockchain platform for converting steps into cryptocurrency. STB - utility token - alternate token name. Token was based on Waves platform. Staps-miner - this is a man who installed application for converting steps into cryptocurrency.  White Paper: White Paper EN  Referral program https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2875135.new#new  How to buy STAPS tokens? https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2966185.new#new  Token description:    Logo: http://www.staps.io/img/logo.png  The project area: Loyalty program, health.  Short desription: Staps-miners will recieved own tokens each week. These tokens staps-miners will exchange from business for discounts and bonuses. Business can spend received tokens from staps-miners in auctions. Each auction will distribute places for ads between participants of auctions. Than more tokens buisness will spend on auction, than better place it will recieved and than more staps-miners will know about buisness offers.   People are walk and recieve staps -> people are change staps tokens to bonuses and discount from buisness -> buisness spend recived from people and bought on exchanges tokens for own promotion to staps-miners.  The Token Cost catalizator: Buisness will need to buy tokens in two cases: 1. 1000 STB tokens for activating buisness account in Staps Platform 2. For winning at auctions   Staps mission: EXTRACTION OF BENEFITS FROM PHYSICAL ACTIVITY CONNECTING BUSINESS TO THE WORLD OF CRYPTOCURRENCY TRANSACTIONS ENSURING HIGH MARKET DEMAND FOR STAPS TOKEN  Site: http://www.staps.io  What's done for today: The prototype application for steps convertation to cryptocurrency was created. Only for russian users at this time, but in the nearest feature will be for english wolrd - Android и нa ios. More than 10000 active users at this time.  The target audience: Business that need of attracting new customers and retaining existing. People that searching  to benefits from walking.  Is blockchain technology used? Is there any sense in implementing this idea on the blockchain: Each Staps token can be put on the crypto exchanges. All transactions in Staps Platfrom will be provided in blockchain, that will support micro transactions, but until then all transaction will be in Staps Plotform servers.    Start tokens sale: 18.02.2018  What profits will be earned and it is earned now: Profit will be from comissions for withdrawal to waves platform and for placement offers from buisness,  Interest for infrastructure not related to blockchain: Staps Platform is a big interest for buisness such loyality program. Staps-miners will be very motivated for spending own tokens with real moneys.  Tokens count: Common count - 1 000 000 000 STB Sale count - 60 000 000 STB.  Roadmap: Q3 2016 - Start of the team building and development of the initial idea. Q1 2017 – Creation of the alpha version of the application and internal testing. Q2 2017 - Beta version. Working out the calculation and exchange of coins between users. Q3 2017 - Application set up and preparation for the ICO. Q4 2017 - Team Formation and creation of White Paper. Q1 2018 - Start and completion of the crowdfunding campaign and release of the STB token to the stock exchange. Q2 2018 - Ecosystem development and null emissions for early users. Q3 2018 - Beta version of the platform and functionality for the business. Q4 2018 - >10 000 000 users and implementation of the main components of the platform.   pre-ICO Token cost on: 1 STB = 0,2 USD  Is exists first clients? Small buisness in Russia, over 10000 active users.
